      <title>土耳其经济复苏信心增强 吸引投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/turkey-woos-investors-with-faith-in-economic-turnaround-growing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者对土耳其经济实力的押注日益增加，以及该国长达一年的回归传统政策的延续，土耳其正在赢得投资者的青睐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/turkey-woos-investors-with-faith-in-economic-turnaround-growing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 14:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
